        <p
          class='font-bestoom bg-25-accent text-25-primary relative z-10 mx-auto w-fit px-6 pt-2 pb-0.5 text-center text-2xl tracking-wide uppercase shadow-lg shadow-black/20 md:pt-3 md:text-4xl'>
          Convocatoria cerrada
        </p>

        <p
          class='font-dk text-25-white bg-25-blue mx-auto w-fit -skew-y-[4deg] px-6 py-2 text-center text-2xl leading-none tracking-wide shadow-lg shadow-black/20 md:py-3 md:text-4xl'>
